Comment: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸也不是很清楚
Comment: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好啦 不久葉卡醫生就要來了
Comment: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳問看看醫生吧
Comment: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哦 好像來了
Comment: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來了
Comment: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎?
Comment: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的 跟你同年紀的女孩子
Comment: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這附近沒有小孩子
Comment: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們要好好相處
Comment: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也要看她的態度再說了
Comment: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就是因為這樣 才一個朋友都交不到
Comment: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪 不在家嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼先生
Comment: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是葉卡
Comment: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不好意思
Comment: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒救了
Comment: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 在這附近有看到小女孩嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有看到米卡莎嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有
Comment: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎
Comment: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸去把憲兵團叫來 要求搜索
Comment: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在山麓那等著
Comment: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,知道了嗎? 艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她真的可以賣出去嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,特地把她的爸媽殺了 還把她抓來
Comment: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你仔細看看她的臉
Comment: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是還不錯
Comment: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過還是小鬼
Comment: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是我的菜
Comment: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不是在問是不是你的菜
Comment: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她是「東洋人」
Comment: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以前人類也有所謂的種族
Comment: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而她是從前從「東洋」逃進來城牆內的最後末裔啊
Comment: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把她帶到王都的地下黑市
Comment: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓那些色老頭來競標
Comment: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其他東洋人都已經滅絕了
Comment: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她一定可以賣個好價錢
Comment: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她的父親可不像是東洋人
Comment: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她不是純種
Comment: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對啊
Comment: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真正有價值的是媽媽
Comment: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都是因為你害怕而出手殺了她
Comment: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是沒辦法的啊
Comment: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰叫她反抗
Comment: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想說的只有這些嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,葉卡醫生 我們等你很久...
Comment: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不好意思打擾囉
Comment: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我安份一點
Comment: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不想腦袋被這個劈成兩半的話
Comment: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個女人
Comment: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快逃
Comment: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,媽媽
Comment: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎 快點
Comment: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個...
