Comment: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是醫生葉卡的兒子
Comment: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳之前應該有見過我爸
