Comment: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個世界
Comment: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是殘酷的
Comment: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這瞬間 我身體的顫抖停止了
Comment: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從那時開始
Comment: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經可以完全控制自己
Comment: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得我自己什麼都辦得到
