Comment: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們只是剛好和人長得一樣的野獸
Comment: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算這時候憲兵團的人趕到
Comment: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們也早就離開了
Comment: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本趕不上
Comment: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是這樣好了
Comment: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只是你運氣好罷了 艾連
