Comment: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還記得我嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳還小的時候 見過幾次
Comment: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,葉卡醫生
Comment: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以後該往哪裡才能夠回家?
Comment: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好冷...
Comment: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經...
Comment: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有可以回去的地方了
Comment: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給妳
Comment: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很溫暖吧?
Comment: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好溫暖
Comment: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來我們的家裡一起生活吧
Comment: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生了這麼多傷心的事情
Comment: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳需要足夠的休息
Comment: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點走吧
Comment: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回到我們的家
Comment: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回去...
Comment: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有勝利的人才能夠存活的
Comment: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,殘酷世界
Comment: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該撤退了! 阿卡曼
Comment: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要爬上城牆了
Comment: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我去支援前衛的撤退
Comment: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 阿卡曼!
Comment: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是對我而言
Comment: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這個世界還有我要回去的地方
Comment: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有你在
Comment: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就無所不能
Comment: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對我而言
Comment: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有要回去的地方
Comment: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結束護衛任務後
Comment: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,著急的趕去艾連身旁的米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等待著她的是...
Comment: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「艾連的死訊」
