Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 怎麼了 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你回神了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:01:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有受傷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你那一班呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}班...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂喂! 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼只有你一個人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且總覺得你身上黏黏的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底發生了什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我這個廢物去死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.45,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 冷靜點阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:25.76,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}夠了吧 柯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全滅了啦 除了這傢伙以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏可什麼都還沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看看周圍就能知道了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們可沒時間繼續管這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會只有阿爾敏沒事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定被當做是屍體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然遇上多名巨人讓人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過竟然只有這個爛學生存活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他們一定死不瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要我讓妳永遠無法再說話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家情緒都不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟突然間大家的朋友們都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真不愧是我的克里斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等這場戰役結束後我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}的確...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們比之前更加囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之我們不能維持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還站得起來嗎? 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉... 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去跟後衛會合...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂... 阿爾敏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走囉 柯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們奉命要繼續前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是變成了地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是之前都搞錯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打從一開始這個世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:03:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再也簡單了解不過的世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}試圖在這個世界中...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓自己變得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}進而拯救了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}軟弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這點讓我無法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對他們倆而言...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是要被保護的存在...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想和他們兩個一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能夠肩並肩地...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一起活在...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界上...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但如今結果卻是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}害得艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏你幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲沒有呼吸了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從剛才就對他...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做了好幾次好幾次的心肺復甦術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲他...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢娜 這裡太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點去屋頂...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.34,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不能丟下法蘭茲不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是這樣的漢娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要再試了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼做...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼做都...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 我說你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道沒有搞懂現在是什麼情況嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是知道 才會變成這樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你們想要活 就給我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別鬧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.44,Default,q,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼推 也過不去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.06,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣我們不就會被巨人吃掉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在搞什麼? 士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快去制止他們啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可...可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有種就試試啊 菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是這裡商會的老大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也不想想是誰給你們這些士兵東西吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有辦法養活這裡全部的士兵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們也給我推!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這些東西是你們用一輩子也賺不到的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要願意幫忙 就有賞!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒問題的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸會用大砲把他們做掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繼續推!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不想死的傢伙就給我推!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼無視我們啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是奇行種!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想再多也沒用!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太快了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連我們精銳部隊都追不上...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們... 在幹什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來的正好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳快叫他們來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}賞不會少給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的夥伴們一直在犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為居民還沒有完成避難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只好跟巨人戰鬥並且犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是當然的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了保護居民的生命財產
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}獻出心臟不就是你們的職責嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃免錢的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好不容易在百年間有一次機會能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是在跩三小啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你認為為了別人而死是理所當然的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那你一定可以理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個人珍貴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可以拯救眾人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳給我試試看啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我和妳的上司是老朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些士兵的前途 我隨便都能決定的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你要屍體怎樣說話?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會長...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把台車拉出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大姊姊 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}託妳的福 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真虧妳能收拾掉他 阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我太急於一口氣擊殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而讓刀刃變鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下次我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳之前到底經歷過怎樣的經驗...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不... 沒事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼這個時候會想起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哎呀 做得真好呢 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個刺繡是我們一族代代相傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等到米卡莎有了自己的孩子 我就教妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小孩要怎樣才會有呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿災 妳去問爸爸看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好啦 不久葉卡醫生就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳問看看醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哦 好像來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的 跟你同年紀的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為這附近沒有小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也要看她的態度再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就是因為這樣 才一個朋友都交不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪 不在家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 在這附近有看到小女孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有看到米卡莎嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸去把憲兵團叫來 要求搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在山麓那等著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}知道了嗎? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她真的可以賣出去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}特地把她的爸媽殺了 還把她抓來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你仔細看看她的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過還是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是在問是不是你的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她是「東洋人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以前人類也有所謂的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而她是從前從「東洋」逃進來城牆內的最後末裔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把她帶到王都的地下黑市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓那些色老頭來競標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其他東洋人都已經滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她一定可以賣個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的父親可不像是東洋人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她不是純種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真正有價值的是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都是因為你害怕而出手殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰叫她反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想說的只有這些嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡醫生 我們等你很久...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思打擾囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我安份一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不想腦袋被這個劈成兩半的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡 給我適可而止點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛? 不是說了要殺的只有父親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是 這個女人她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別找藉口了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把小孩給我抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 妳最好給我安份點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然 就會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好冷...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是怎麼找到這的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個... 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...在森林裡迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看到了這間小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小孩子獨自在森林裡遊盪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}森林裡可是有可怕的大野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過你不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要跟叔叔一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}像你們這種人就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會這樣是活該!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要再給我站起來了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是米卡莎對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是醫生葉卡的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳之前應該有見過我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我陪我爸出診來到妳家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結果...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該有三個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你幹的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你幹的嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我宰了你 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不戰...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只有死...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}贏了話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就能活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個死小孩到底在說些什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不戰鬥的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就打不贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我辦不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個景象我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}見過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論何時都在我的眼中呈現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我卻當作沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這瞬間 我身體的顫抖停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從那時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經可以完全控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得我自己什麼都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要戰鬥!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從背後朝著心臟直接刺進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是那兩個小孩幹的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是叫你在山麓等我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你知道你自己做了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我殺了有害的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們只是剛好和人長得一樣的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算這時候憲兵團的人趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們也早就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根本趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只是你運氣好罷了 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我責罵的是你太不重視自己的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只是想快點救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還記得我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳還小的時候 見過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以後該往哪裡才能夠回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好冷...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有可以回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很溫暖吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來我們的家裡一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生了這麼多傷心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳需要足夠的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回到我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回去...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有勝利的人才能夠存活的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殘酷世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該撤退了! 阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要爬上城牆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去支援前衛的撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 阿卡曼!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這個世界還有我要回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有要回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束護衛任務後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}著急的趕去艾連身旁的米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等待著她的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「艾連的死訊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
